545
00:43:38,730 --> 00:43:41,230
<i>was not a failure.</i>

546
00:43:55,580 --> 00:43:56,980
Excuse me.

547
00:44:04,520 --> 00:44:07,120
<i>Even if I can't achieve all of that,</i>

548
00:44:07,460 --> 00:44:08,720
I'm sorry.

549
00:44:09,060 --> 00:44:10,290
<i>I would have</i>

550
00:44:10,690 --> 00:44:13,460
<i>one or two in my grip</i>

551
00:44:20,300 --> 00:44:23,840
<i>- and be envious of what I can't have.
