552
00:44:32,050 --> 00:44:34,450
<i>- I thought that would be me at forty.
- (Jeong Ah-ran: Born August 7, 1969)</i>

553
00:44:42,210 --> 00:44:44,030
<i>("Notes on Life")
(Author: Jeong Ah-ran)</i>

554
00:44:44,030 --> 00:44:46,210
<i>- I thought it wouldn't do if it wasn't that.
