670
00:56:22,690 --> 00:56:24,120
That's good news.

671
00:56:24,960 --> 00:56:25,990
Right.

672
00:56:27,490 --> 00:56:28,930
Give me one, too.

673
00:56:31,700 --> 00:56:34,270
There's nothing like
gummy bears to relieve stress.

674
00:56:35,070 --> 00:56:36,240
Right.

675
00:56:38,940 --> 00:56:40,040
But is it

676
00:56:41,780 --> 00:56:44,140
okay to not ask why she'll be late?

677
00:56:45,750 --> 00:56:47,250
She works.

678
00:56:48,450 --> 00:56:50,380
So she can be late sometimes.

679
00:56:53,050 --> 00:56:54,320
Right?

680
00:56:55,360 --> 00:56:56,360
Of course.

681
00:56:57,090 --> 00:56:59,090
Wouldn't it be weirder
if you suddenly asked?

682
00:57:01,200 --> 00:57:02,530
Right.

683
00:58:04,120 --> 00:58:05,990
<i>When I become forty one day,</i>

684
00:58:09,190 --> 00:58:11,000
<i>I'd have a high-rise apartment
that overlooks</i>

685
00:58:11,000 --> 00:58:12,430
<i>the entire city.</i>

686
00:58:14,470 --> 00:58:17,340
<i>A smart wife who is
different from me in every way.</i>

687
00:58:19,040 --> 00:58:21,170
<i>A kid who is clean and pure</i>

688
00:58:21,170 --> 00:58:22,760
<i>like he just got out of the bath.</i>

689
00:58:25,980 --> 00:58:29,680
<i>A restaurant in Gangnam to my name</i>

690
00:58:29,680 --> 00:58:30,990
<i>that sells food and drinks.</i>

691
00:58:48,640 --> 00:58:51,210
<i>When I become forty one day,</i>

692
00:58:52,170 --> 00:58:54,980
<i>and I've failed to achieve
even one of these...</i>

693
00:59:03,640 --> 00:59:04,700
<i>And I still</i>

694
00:59:05,590 --> 00:59:06,920
<i>must live like this,</i>

695
00:59:08,920 --> 00:59:11,190
<i>like my mom and Father,</i>

696
00:59:13,530 --> 00:59:15,960
<i>only getting poorer</i>

697
00:59:15,960 --> 00:59:18,270
<i>every day,</i>

698
00:59:19,230 --> 00:59:20,230
<i>then</i>

699
00:59:23,200 --> 00:59:27,240
<i>I might become someone
worse than I am now.</i>

700
00:59:35,750 --> 00:59:39,950
<i>(Last Unit:
It's Room 503 at Hotel SHEEM.)</i>

701
00:59:43,160 --> 00:59:44,320
<i>However,</i>

702
00:59:45,290 --> 00:59:48,030
<i>despite all that,
