703
00:59:49,860 --> 00:59:51,130
<i>why</i>

704
00:59:52,900 --> 00:59:55,240
<i>you wanted to give up on life,</i>

705
00:59:59,340 --> 01:00:01,270
<i>why you wanted to leave here,</i>

706
01:00:07,450 --> 01:00:10,580
<i>where you wanted to go after you left...</i>

707
01:00:12,690 --> 01:00:15,720
<i>I don't understand at all.</i>

708
01:00:28,840 --> 01:00:32,240
<i>I don't understand and I don't know.</i>

709
01:00:59,570 --> 01:01:01,440
<i>Where were you trying to go?</i>

710
01:01:05,170 --> 01:01:08,180
<i>Where did you want to go?</i>

