01:01:56,890 --> 01:01:58,490
<i>Why did you call me?</i>

717
01:01:59,490 --> 01:02:00,660
<i>What you want to do.</i>

718
01:02:01,060 --> 01:02:03,230
<i>You remember Min-jeong, right?</i>

719
01:02:03,230 --> 01:02:06,030
<i>We were talking on the phone
