720
01:02:06,030 --> 01:02:07,670
<i>I called again but she's not picking up.</i>

721
01:02:07,670 --> 01:02:10,200
<i>You wore clothes
your father-in-law bought you</i>

722
01:02:10,200 --> 01:02:12,640
<i>whenever you met me?</i>

723
01:02:13,340 --> 01:02:15,680
<i>You've nothing to say, right?
